news.title: Greater Noida authority allots Rs 500 crore for airport, Rs 1,200 crore for land acquisition
news.para: ​Overall, a budget of Rs 4,859 crore was approved for 2024-25 for GNIDA during its 134th Board Meeting held in Greater Noida.

news.title: NGT asks Ghaziabad DM to ascertain correct position of residential construction on land that's part of lake
news.para: The NGT was hearing a plea claiming that a project of Mahalaxmi Land and Finance Company was being built on a lake area in violation of environmental norms.

news.title: Telangana PCB slaps notice on Ananda Homes & Pooja Homes for encroaching Neknampur lake
news.para: The firms were found to have unlawfully encroached upon the lake and disposed of debris into it without authorisation, officials stated.

news.title: Over 1,700 defaulters owe Pune civic body Rs 5,000 crore in property tax
news.para: According to the data revealed under RTI, almost 94 property owners went to court against the dues, which amount to Rs 988 crore, of which Rs 565 crore is from two owners. In addition, tax from mobile towers amounts to Rs2,427 crore.

news.title: Navi Mumbai: Environmentalists concerned as draft DP opens 'flamingo lake' area for development
news.para: While NMMC has clarified that it is a draft DP and not the final report, and that they have only included the updated Cidco nodal plan, greens opine that the ‘flamingo lake’ area should have been reserved as a no-development zone.

news.title: Mumbai: Beauvue Stiledivita directors booked for cutting corners on interiors of Worli flat
news.para: EOW files FIR, directors deny allegations. Rs 80 crore apartment on Dr Annie Besant Road. Complainant alleges breach of contract, advance payment, and inspection issues. Selection of marble, granite, and furniture involved.

news.title: Eligible or not, Dharavi redevelopment for all slum dwellers: Maharashtra CM
news.para: “See the condition in which people live. Govt will give homes to eligible slum dwellers and ineligible slum dwellers will also get homes,” Shinde in the state assembly.

news.title: Rise in unauthorised constructions due to flaws in urban housing policies: SC
news.para: ​Acknowledging that the right to have a roof over head is a fundamental right, the top court said there is a huge gap in the policies between the requirements of the economically weaker sections and what the government was doing at the ground level.

news.title: Uttar Pradesh government wants 3-4 lakh registries done in four months in Noida
news.para: Singh, who is also the chairman of the Noida and the Greater Noida authorities, said Chief Minister Yogi Adityanath will visit Gautam Buddh Nagar between March 7 and 10 to take stock of the situation.

news.title: Saint-Gobain aims for double-digit operating margin in 2024
news.para: In a call with journalists, Bazin added that there is a "structural unmet need for housing" in Western Europe, North America and Asia, which could reverse the new-construction division's downward curb.

news.title: Spain's Inmobiliaria Colonial reports net loss of $1.10 billion in 2023
news.para: Real estate companies such as Colonial and its peer Merlin Properties earn profit on the rental of their assets and have to include in their results the impact of an updated valuation of their properties conducted every six months.

news.title: Ireland: Glenveagh Properties & Cairn Homes eye big growth in state-partnered projects
news.para: Despite recovering to a 15-year high of almost 33,000 units last year, new housing supply in Ireland has for a decade failed to keep up with demand. Analysts say closer to 50,000 homes are needed a year as the economy and population grows strongly.

news.title: New home prices in China rise by 0.14% in February 2024: Survey
news.para: The average new home price across 100 cities rose 0.14%, compared with an on-month gain of 0.15% in January, showed data from real estate researcher China Index Academy.

news.title: Evos Alchemy: Elevating luxury living in Odisha by  Evos Buildcon Pvt Ltd
news.para: Developed by Evos Buildcon Pvt Ltd, this visionary project promises residents a lifestyle of gold-class living, reshaping the future of real estate in Odisha and beyond.

news.title: Deutsche Bank to file liquidation suit against China's Shimao Group: Sources
news.para: Shanghai-based Shimao is among the many Chinese developers that have defaulted on offshore bonds, after it missed the interest and principal payment for a $1 billion offshore bond in July, 2022.

news.title: China Evergrande chairman's second seized Hong Kong mansion put up for sale
news.para: Evergrande, the world's most indebted property developer which defaulted its offshore debt in late 2021, was liquidated by a Hong Kong court in January.

news.title: China sets deadline for cities to set up financing coordination mechanism for property projects
news.para: Financial institutions need to prevent loans from being misappropriated and safeguard the safety of credit funds, the Chinese housing ministry's newspaper China Real Estate Business reported, citing a meeting held on Thursday.

news.title: Trinity Infratech partners with Seetu Kohli to bring one-of-a-kind residences furnished with Versace homes to Gurgaon
news.para: Seetu Kohli, a prominent name in India's design fraternity, brings her impeccable taste and vision to this project, ensuring that every aspect of the residence exudes elegance and luxury.

news.title: Maharashtra government plans transit-oriented development near metro, monorail stations
news.para: The state government plans to increase footfalls in Metro and monorail by introducing a new regulation for transit-oriented development (TOD) zones.
